<h1 class="govuk-heading-l">This service is not available</h1>

<div class="govuk-grid-row">
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    <div class="govuk-body">
      There are a few reasons that may explain why you are seeing this page:
    </div>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <div class="govuk-body">
          you work in a women's or open prison, the service is currently only available for the male closed estate
        </div>
      </li>
      <li>
        <div class="govuk-body">
          you work in more than one prison, and have not been given access to the service for both prisons
          (check which prison you're signed in to in digital prison services)
        </div>
      </li>
      <li>
        <div class="govuk-body">
          you need to have the 'Allocation case manager' role added in digital prison services by your local system
          administrator (LSA) following <%= link_to 'these instructions', help_step2_path %>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li>
        <div class="govuk-body">
          you need to have the PRO (Prison Officer) or PO (Probation Officer) role added in NOMIS by your local
          system administrator (LSA) following <%= link_to 'these instructions', help_step3_path %>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li>
        <div class="govuk-body">
          you entered an incorrect web address
        </div>
      </li>
    </ul>
    <div class="govuk-body">
      If you don't think any of these reasons apply to you, contact the <%= link_to 'allocations service team', contact_us_path %>.
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
